    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Facebook AI Research (or FAIR ‚Ä¶ how humble) is no strange to this kind of learning. In fact, in December 2021 they released the famous <a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/2111.06377.pdf" target="_self">Masked Autoencoders</a> that uses a simpler but similar method to learn representations of images in a Self-Supervised way.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
